    {"children":[{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我以为你不来了"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":" (wǒ yǐ wéi nǐ bù lái le) - \"I thought you weren't coming\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以为是真的"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":" (yǐ wéi shì zhēn de) - \"thought it was true\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你以为呢？"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":" (nǐ yǐ wéi ne?) - \"what do you think?\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以为自己很聪明"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":" (yǐ wéi zì jǐ hěn cōng míng) - \"think oneself very smart\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"别以为我不知道"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":" (bié yǐ wéi wǒ bù zhī dào) - \"don't think I don't know\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"}],"ordered":false,"spread":false,"start":null,"type":"list"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Grammar Patterns"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以为 typically:"}],"type":"paragraph"},
    {"children":[{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"With clauses"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 以为他走了 - \"thought he had left\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mistaken assumptions"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 以为很容易 - \"thought it was easy\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Past assumptions"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 原来以为 - \"originally thought\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Questions"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 你以为怎么样？ - \"what do you think?\""}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"}],"ordered":false,"spread":false,"start":null,"type":"list"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cultural Context"}],"depth":2,"type":"heading"},
    {"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以为 reflects Chinese epistemology:"}],"type":"paragraph"},
    {"children":[{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Humility about knowledge"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 以为 acknowledges human fallibility"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Learning from mistakes"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": Recognizing when 以为 was wrong leads to wisdom"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Social awareness"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": Understanding that others may 以为 things about you"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Critical thinking"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": 以为 reminds us to question our assumptions"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"},{"checked":null,"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Face-saving"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","value":": Using 以为 can soften admissions of being wrong"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"spread":false,"type":"listItem"}],"ordered":false,"spread":false,"start":null,"type":"list"}
